07:54.940 --> 07:59.580
One of the reasons for this drop in prices is the rise of efficient airplanes.

07:59.580 --> 08:05.220
Certain innovations such as composite construction, better aerodynamics, more efficient engines,

08:05.220 --> 08:10.020
